      <section class="content" id="howtoplay">
        <div class="sub">
          <div data-delighter class="delighter-left image" style="background-image:url(img/2_ipad_white_portrait.png)"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="sub">
          <h2>How to play Quento</h2>
          <p>See that <b>8</b> above the game board? To make it, you need <b>three</b> numbers. Try this:</p>
          <q>6 + 7 - 5</q>
          <p>Can you make that <b>11</b> by using <b>four</b> numbers?</p>
          <p>You're playing Quento!</p>
        </div>
        <div data-delighter class="centered stars">
          <br><br>
          <div class="icon star star-1 light"></div>
          <div class="icon star star-2 light"></div>
          <div class="icon star star-3 light"></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content" id="mentalcalculation">
        <div class="sub">
          <h2>Enjoy mental calculation</h2>
          <p>Take your time to find the solution. There's a challenge for everyone. Without pressure.</p>
          <p>You decide when to start the next round. And if you get stuck, a subtle hint will guide you without spoiling the fun.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sub">
          <div data-delighter class="image delighter-scale" style="background-image:url(img/4_iphone_white_angle1.png)"></div>
        </div>
      </section>

